flowchart TB
    I[Intent] -->|MOTIVATES| EC[Engineering Change]
    A[Actor] -->|PARTICIPATES_IN| EC
    A -->|PERFORMS| ACT[Activity]
    ACT -->|AFFECTS| AR[Artifact]
    AR -->|IMPLEMENTS| EC

    REV[Review] -->|REVIEWS| EC
    REV -->|PRODUCES| F[Finding]
    ACT -->|ADDRESSES| F

    V[Validation Run] -->|VALIDATES| AR
    V -->|VALIDATES| EC
    B[Build] -->|BUILDS_FROM| AR
    B -->|PRODUCES_ARTIFACT| DA[Deployable Artifact]
    D[Deployment] -->|DEPLOYS| DA
    D -->|INCLUDES_CHANGE| EC
    R[Release] -->|EXPOSES| POP[Population]
    D --> R

    EC -->|RESULTS_IN| O[Outcome]
    EC -->|CONTRIBUTES_TO| INC[Incident]
    EXP[Experiment] -->|ASSIGNS| EC
    EXP --> EX[Exposure]
    EX --> EC
    EVID[Evidence] -->|INFORMS| DEC[Decision]
    EC --> EVID
    O --> EVID

    P[Provenance, confidence, time, and version] -. applies to .-> EC
    P -. applies to .-> ACT
    P -. applies to .-> D
    P -. applies to .-> O
